Resource Profile: BundleAgregateur

Official URL: http://sas.fr/fhir/StructureDefinition/BundleAgregateur Version: 1.0.0
Active as of 2024-11-18 Computable Name: BundleAgregateur

Profil de Bundle qui représente le flux de réponse contenant les créneaux disponibles dans le cadre du service d’agrégation de créneaux de la plateforme SAS (Service d’accès aux soins)

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Bundle/ExampleBundlePSIndiv

Formal Views of Profile Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.

IdGradePath(s)DetailsRequirements
bdl-1errorBundletotal only when a search or history
: total.empty() or (type = 'searchset') or (type = 'history')
bdl-2errorBundleentry.search only when a search
: entry.search.empty() or (type = 'searchset')
bdl-3errorBundleentry.request mandatory for batch/transaction/history, otherwise prohibited
: entry.all(request.exists() = (%resource.type = 'batch' or %resource.type = 'transaction' or %resource.type = 'history'))
bdl-4errorBundleentry.response mandatory for batch-response/transaction-response/history, otherwise prohibited
: entry.all(response.exists() = (%resource.type = 'batch-response' or %resource.type = 'transaction-response' or %resource.type = 'history'))
bdl-5errorBundle.entry, Bundle.entry:FrSlotAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrScheduleAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateurmust be a resource unless there's a request or response
: resource.exists() or request.exists() or response.exists()
bdl-7errorBundleFullUrl must be unique in a bundle, or else entries with the same fullUrl must have different meta.versionId (except in history bundles)
: (type = 'history') or entry.where(fullUrl.exists()).select(fullUrl&resource.meta.versionId).isDistinct()
bdl-8errorBundle.entry, Bundle.entry:FrSlotAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrScheduleAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateurfullUrl cannot be a version specific reference
: fullUrl.contains('/_history/').not()
bdl-9errorBundleA document must have an identifier with a system and a value
: type = 'document' implies (identifier.system.exists() and identifier.value.exists())
bdl-10errorBundleA document must have a date
: type = 'document' implies (timestamp.hasValue())
bdl-11errorBundleA document must have a Composition as the first resource
: type = 'document' implies entry.first().resource.is(Composition)
bdl-12errorBundleA message must have a MessageHeader as the first resource
: type = 'message' implies entry.first().resource.is(MessageHeader)
ele-1error**ALL** elementsAll FHIR elements must have a @value or children
: hasValue() or (children().count() > id.count())
ext-1errorBundle.entry.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry.search.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry.request.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry.response.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrSlotAgregateur.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrSlotAgregateur.search.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrSlotAgregateur.request.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrSlotAgregateur.response.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrScheduleAgregateur.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrScheduleAgregateur.search.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrScheduleAgregateur.request.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrScheduleAgregateur.response.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerAgregateur.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerAgregateur.search.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerAgregateur.request.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerAgregateur.response.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateur.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateur.search.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateur.request.modifierExtension, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateur.response.modifierExtensionMust have either extensions or value[x], not both
: extension.exists() != value.exists()

IdGradePath(s)DetailsRequirements
bdl-1errorBundletotal only when a search or history
: total.empty() or (type = 'searchset') or (type = 'history')
bdl-2errorBundleentry.search only when a search
: entry.search.empty() or (type = 'searchset')
bdl-3errorBundleentry.request mandatory for batch/transaction/history, otherwise prohibited
: entry.all(request.exists() = (%resource.type = 'batch' or %resource.type = 'transaction' or %resource.type = 'history'))
bdl-4errorBundleentry.response mandatory for batch-response/transaction-response/history, otherwise prohibited
: entry.all(response.exists() = (%resource.type = 'batch-response' or %resource.type = 'transaction-response' or %resource.type = 'history'))
bdl-5errorBundle.entry, Bundle.entry:FrSlotAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrScheduleAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateurmust be a resource unless there's a request or response
: resource.exists() or request.exists() or response.exists()
bdl-7errorBundleFullUrl must be unique in a bundle, or else entries with the same fullUrl must have different meta.versionId (except in history bundles)
: (type = 'history') or entry.where(fullUrl.exists()).select(fullUrl&resource.meta.versionId).isDistinct()
bdl-8errorBundle.entry, Bundle.entry:FrSlotAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrScheduleAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerAgregateur, Bundle.entry:FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateurfullUrl cannot be a version specific reference
: fullUrl.contains('/_history/').not()
bdl-9errorBundleA document must have an identifier with a system and a value
: type = 'document' implies (identifier.system.exists() and identifier.value.exists())
bdl-10errorBundleA document must have a date

: type = 'document' implies entry.first().resource.is(Composition)
bdl-12errorBundleA message must have a MessageHeader as the first resource
